nodes.template:
Generate an emergency rollback runbook.

Alert: {{alertType}}
Blast Radius: {{blastRadius}}
Recent Change: {{recentChange}}
Can Rollback: {{canRollback}}

Include:
1. Pre-rollback checks (active connections, in-flight requests)
2. Rollback command sequence for CI/CD pipeline
3. Database migration rollback considerations
4. Cache invalidation steps
5. Health check verification post-rollback
6. Stakeholder communication template
7. Time-to-mitigate SLO tracking

Generate a feature flag kill-switch procedure.

Alert: {{alertType}}
Blast Radius: {{blastRadius}}
Recent Change: {{recentChange}}

Include:
1. Identify the feature flag or config change to disable
2. Flag toggle procedure (LaunchDarkly / Azure App Config / env var)
3. Verify traffic stops hitting the broken path
4. Monitor error rates for 5 minutes post-toggle
5. Communicate status to stakeholders
